Dia. 01 A is 2 points
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black plays at 1 (A), Black's territory has increased by 2 points.
\par One captured stone and one point makes 2 points.
\par
\par If White plays at 1, White's territory doesn't increase.
\par Therefore either Black or White plays at \b A\b0 , it is \b 2 points\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
