Dia.02 B is 3 Points
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Let's check the value of Black 1 (\b B\b0 ).
\par After Black cuts White's stone, Black's territory has increased by 3 points. (one captured stone and 2 points)
\par
\par Nobody should forget that there is one point at X.
\par
\par }
