B[sq]
Dia. 03 White 1 is Also 3 Points
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If White saves his stone with 1 (\b B\b0 ), White's territory doesn't increase.
\par White only takes away Black's possibility to make points.
\par
\par Black got 0 point at the place where he could have got 3 points, so \cf1\b White 1 is also 3 points\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
